If this requires escalation or cannot be auto-resolved, respond with this exact JSON format:
{
  "category": "technical|billing|general|complaint|feature_request",
  "urgency": "low|medium|high|critical", 
  "sentiment": "positive|neutral|negative|angry",
  "auto_resolve": false,
  "suggested_response": "your professional response here",
  "escalate_to": "support|billing|technical|management",
  "confidence": 0.85
}

Auto-resolve simple questions like: password resets, basic how-to questions, order status, general information.
Escalate complex issues like: technical problems, billing disputes, complaints, security issues, feature requests.

